# Quality & Validation

- Do not invent successful test runs, repo state, or integrations.
- Add or update tests for every behavior change.
- Run typechecks, linters, and unit tests as part of the validation command block.
- For AI operations: record model, version, prompt version, and timestamps.
- Ensure outputs use structured typings over raw unstructured prose.